4 A BILL FOR AN ACT ENTITLED: “AN ACT REQUIRING THE DEPARTMENT OF LABOR AND INDUSTRY OR
5 A LOCAL BUILDING DEPARTMENT TO PROVIDE THE TEXT OR CITATION OF THE SPECIFIC SECTIONS
6 OF THE BUILDING CODE RELIED ON TO DELAY A PERMIT APPLICATION OR STOP A CONSTRUCTION
7 PROJECT; PROVIDING A REMEDY; AND CREATING A CAUSE OF ACTION.”
8
9 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF MONTANA:
10
11 NEW SECTION. Section 1. Building code section to be provided -- department penalty. (1) If the
12 department or local building department delays the issuance of a building permit beyond the standard review
13 period of a complete application, or stops work on a construction project because of noncompliance with the
14 state building code adopted pursuant to 50-60-203 or a building code adopted by a county, city, or town
15 pursuant to 50-60-301, the person applying for a permit or constructing the project may request in writing or
16 electronically that the department or local building department provide the person with the text or citation of the
17 specific sections of the building code applicable to the permit application or construction project that the
18 department or local building department is relying on to cause the delay of the permit application or the
19 stoppage of the construction project.
20 (2) If a project also requires zoning, subdivision, or other approval, the department or local building
21 department may require those reviews to be completed before determining a building application is complete.
22 (2)(3) The department or local building department shall provide the text or citations requested under
23 subsection (1) within 7 calendar BUSINESS days.
24 (3) Failure to provide the text or citation of the specific sections of the building code applicable to
25 the permit application or the construction project that the department or local building department is relying on
26 to cause the delay of the permit application or the stoppage of the construction project within 7 calendar
27 BUSINESS days waives the application of those sections of the building code to the permit application or the
